snippet.title: Radiohead - Burn The Witch | Funk AI Cover
snippet.description:
Burn The Witch by Radiohead twisted into funk

Like what you hear? Help keep the party going!
https://tiptopjar.com/TwistedMusicStudio

Lyrics:

Stay in the shadows
Cheer at the gallows
This is a round-up

Burn the witch
Burn the witch

Red crosses on wooden doors
If you float, you burn
Loose talk around tables
Abandon all reason
Avoid all eye contact
Do not react
Shoot the messengers

Sing the song of sixpence that goes

Burn the witch
Burn the witch
We know where you live
